data.description: Welcome home to this charming 3-bedroom, 2.5 bath two-story residence in the Solana Ridge subdivision, conveniently located near Lackland, AFB making it an ideal residence for military personnel or those who appreciate proximity to this significant military hub.  As you step inside you're greeted by the warm and inviting dining room that flows into the open-concept living area and kitchen, this is the perfect space for entertaining. The kitchen cabinets provide ample storage space along with the walk in pantry. Upstairs, you'll find a tranquil haven with all three bedrooms thoughtfully situated for privacy. The primary bedroom boasts an ensuite bathroom for added convenience. The additional bedrooms are perfect for guests, or transforming into a home office or hobby space. Step outside to your covered patio, providing a cozy retreat for relaxation or outdoor gatherings. The carefully landscaped yard offers a blend of charm and low maintenance, allowing you to enjoy the Texas weather in style.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this your home with easy access to Hwys 410, 90, and 151. Restaurants, shopping and entertainment are in nearby  proximity as well.
